statements: SELECT * FROM token_ownership
SELECT token_id, owner_id FROM token_ownership ORDER BY timestamp DESC
SELECT token_id, owner_id FROM token_ownership WHERE owner_id = 5
SELECT * FROM token_ownership ORDER BY timestamp ASC LIMIT 3
SELECT token_id, owner_id, timestamp FROM token_ownership WHERE token_id = 10
SELECT * FROM token_ownership WHERE owner_id = 10 ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT owner_id, COUNT(token_id) AS token_count FROM token_ownership GROUP BY owner_id HAVING COUNT(token_id) > 1;
SELECT token_id, owner_id, DATE_FORMAT(timestamp, '%Y-%m-%d') AS date FROM token_ownership WHERE token_id IN (1, 2, 3) ORDER BY owner_id ASC;
SELECT TOP 5 token_id, owner_id, timestamp FROM token_ownership WHERE owner_id BETWEEN 5 AND 10 ORDER BY token_id DESC;
SELECT owner_id, MAX(timestamp) AS latest_timestamp FROM token_ownership GROUP BY owner_id ORDER BY latest_timestamp DESC;

SELECT token_id, owner_id FROM tokenized_assets WHERE asset_id > 100 ORDER BY owner_id ASC;

SELECT asset_id, first_name, last_name FROM tokenized_assets JOIN asset_owners ON tokenized_assets.owner_id = asset_owners.owner_id WHERE token_id < 50 ORDER BY asset_id DESC;
SELECT * FROM tokenized_assets WHERE compliance_status='approved' AND token_id BETWEEN 10 AND 20 ORDER BY asset_id;
